  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de kde-base-artwork</title>
    <para>Installez <application>kde-base-artwork</application> en exécutant
    les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>
<screen>
<userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir; -Wno-dev ..</userinput>
</screen>
    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput>
</screen>
  </sect2>
